Package: rKraken
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper for the Kraken Package
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2020-02-24
Authors@R: c(person("Stijn", "van Dongen", role = c("aut"), email = "svd@sanger.ac.uk"),
             person("Gord", "Brown", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "gordon.brown@cruk.cam.ac.uk"))
Description: This package provides three functions, wrapping utilities from
  the Kraken package (https://www.ebi.ac.uk/research/enright/software/kraken).
  "reaper" demultiplexes, trims, and filters short read sequencing data.
  "tally" collapses identical reads to a single entry, recording the number
  of occurrences of each.  "minion" infers the sequence of 3' adapter in
  short read data.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.2)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
